# Vendor Data Processing Agreements (DPA)

This directory holds Data Processing Agreements and related vendor data-handling documentation
for all external systems that process personal or financial data on behalf of the organisation
under the Financial Intelligence Platform (FIP).

**Legal basis:** GDPR Art. 28 (processor agreements), CCPA § 1798.140(v), and Hungarian Act CXII of 2011
on the Right of Informational Self-Determination and on Freedom of Information.

